<lb n="1"/>śrī mūlasaṁgha dēsigaṇa koṁḍakuṁ<note n="344-1">On</note>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>dānvaya postakagacha yiṁgaḷēśvara ba
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ḷiya śrī nēmidēvara guḍugaḷuma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ppa siṁgiseṭṭi dēviseṭṭi padumavve
<lb n="5"/>siṁgeya Ivara niśidhi maṁgaḷa [<g type="ddanda">.</g>] ma
<lb n="6" break="no"/>hā śrī śrī śrī śrī śrī<note n="344-2">Below this in later characters.</note>
